SDMMC004_CSDV1Type Struct Reference

Detailed Description

This structure stores the SD v1 card's Csd register content.

uint32_t SDMMC004_CSDV1Type::CCC

The card command class register CCC defines which command classes are supported by this card.A value of 1 in a CCC bit means that the corresponding command class is supported.

uint32_t SDMMC004_CSDV1Type::WriteProtGrpSize

The size of a write protected group. The actual size is computed by increasing this number by one. A value of zero means one erase sector, 127 means 128 erase sectors.
